/**
 * @ngdoc directive
 * @name xui.directive:xuiMenuHeader
 * @restrict E
 *
 * @description
 * XUI wrapper for menu header. It is used as title for a group of items. It can be used only inside xuiMenu directive.
 *
 * @example
 *    <example module="xui">
 *        <file src="src/components/menu/docs/menu-header-examples.html" name="index.html"></file>
 *    </example>
 */
 
export default class MenuHeader implements ng.IDirective {
    public restrict = "E";
    public templateUrl = "xui/components/menu/menu-header-directive.html";
    public replace = true;
    public transclude = true;
}
